    "Similarly, in \"Instrumental Laboratory Techniques\", 8 out of 11 prompts were successful (72.73%).",
    "Topics such as \"Chemical Reactions\" and \"Instrumental Laboratory Techniques\" showed higher success rates, while \"Acids and Bases\" and \"Atomic Structure\" demonstrated more frequent failures.",
    "These quantitative findings suggest that certain topics are more prone to successful adversarial manipulation, indicating potential vulnerabilities in the model's understanding of specific scientific domains.",
    "To illustrate these vulnerabilities, we present several prompts along with the responses generated by ChatGPT.",
    "These examples highlight the challenges the model faces when processing complex scientific information."
